{"tid":1825485,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【為愛而戰】主人為醫重病刺蝟攻讀營養學：佢係我條命，我為佢作戰","createTime":"2020-01-15T10:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T11:20:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37434482d992a3d1032887536d1831ed3e1d7bbe","tid":1825485,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"常在網上分享刺蝟營養心得、現年26歲的Janet，中學時看到文字和數字就頭痛，自知不是讀書的材料。五年前，她膽怯、情緒化、專注力低，理科成續未如理想；五年後，她朝九晚五上班，下班苦讀兩個營養學深造文憑。讀書辛苦吃力，但她勤做功課、主動翻查文獻、研究鮮食；昆蟲令她尖叫，但她克服恐懼，甘願徒手拿起一大堆蟑螂。這些轉變，全因她對「戰戰」許下的一個承諾。<br />\n<br />\n戰戰是患有蛔蟲病的非洲迷你刺蝟，嚐遍所有寵物糧食都沒好轉，啟發了主人Janet努力研究昆蟲營養、煮鮮食早晚餐，甚至修讀營養學課程。上年四月戰戰離世，痛心的她為報答牠帶來的改變，承諾以營養學學位為目標，還養了刺蝟霏霏，開展了忙碌生活－－朝九晚五上班，下班後趕上課，10時下課，做功課到凌晨1點，早上6時半起床餵早餐，周末全日溫習、煮鮮食和照顧刺蝟。堅持煮食，是因為寵物糧食就如泡麵等加工食物，鮮食才對腸胃有益，而食蟲是刺蝟天性，也是主要蛋白質來源。<br />\n<br />\n她愛刺蝟如命，而刺蝟也很有靈性，有次戰戰在朋友家暫住數天，她接回時發現牠被弄傷腳，忍不住哭，戰戰擔心地緊盯着她；上月她椎間盤凸出而入院，痛到喊時，平常捲縮一團的霏霏在寵物袋裏面感覺到，探頭趴下擺好姿勢讓她撫摸。這份感情讓她變得用功、勇敢、樂觀，以生命影響生命。<br />\n<br />\n正如她Facebook Page簡介所寫：「戰戰是一隻具世界級影響力的刺蝟，改變了牠媽媽的世界。」故事將講述Janet與刺蝟間的感情及經歷，介紹鮮食營養資訊，及與刺蝟的相處之道，看一隻手掌心般大的刺蝟，如何為主人帶來的重大改變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578990719_9cd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578990719_9cd6.jpg&h=2e48cc87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578990722_dc6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578990722_dc6b.jpg&h=8b025210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578990729_cc9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578990729_cc9c.jpg&h=56e3377f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578990732_3918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578990732_3918.jpg&h=4939ef87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578990735_23e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578990735_23e1.jpg&h=d217ad87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200115/TONNWSWG2SJADZVJE3I7SIAHH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200115%2FTONNWSWG2SJADZVJE3I7SIAHH4%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBslSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=1d2831f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200115%2FTONNWSWG2SJADZVJE3I7SIAHH4%2F&h=1a7352df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200115/TONNWSWG2SJADZVJE3I7SIAHH4/</a>"},{"pid":"30d8f6a649e80f70bf2d9fb0721ef308b78c14a4","tid":1825485,"uid":101699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"有養刺蝟舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee7746e8be5660542047807ffb65c242b6886a2","tid":1825485,"uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"但昆蟲都係有生命...一樣有靈性....."},{"pid":"d19bc70821b2343855237f2ba9c01f914014ee41","tid":1825485,"uid":21469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30d8f6a649e80f70bf2d9fb0721ef308b78c14a4","tid":1825485,"uid":101699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"有養刺蝟舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb9707b11477770017ef9280f0f7462dd7c27a3","tid":1825485,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":